metadata.name: Fabian Williams - Multiple Choice Mural #1
metadata.title: The Multiple Choice Mural
metadata.description: Fabian Williams has created a new mural to continue spotlighting racial inequalities in American professional football organizations.  Byron Allen and Brian Flores have been added to this mural, alongside a kneeling Colin Kaepernick, to bring awareness to their causes.  Fabian ended his statement with popular Tik Tok star Khabane Lame simply asking, What Now?  The mural is located in Los Angeles and was completed on February 13th, 2022.  More information can be found at https://fabianwilliams.art
